<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>로그인 | Public</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            color: #111;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #3182f6;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(49,130,246,0.15);
        }
        .btn-login {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background-color: #3182f6;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            background-color: #1e6ff2;
        }
        .extra-links {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        .error {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #ffe2e2;
            color: #c00;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .logout {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #e6f3ff;
            color: #0366d6;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="login-container">
    <div class="title">로그인</div>
    <div class="subtitle">간편하게 로그인하고 서비스를 이용해보세요</div>

    <form action="/login" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="userId">아이디</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>

        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>
    </form>

    {{#param.error}}
        <div class="error">아이디 또는 비밀번호가 잘못되었습니다.</div>
    {{/param.error}}

    {{#param.logout}}
        <div class="logout">로그아웃 되었습니다.</div>
    {{/param.logout}}

    <div class="extra-links">
        아직 계정이 없으신가요? <a href="#" style="color:#3182f6; text-decoration:none;">회원가입</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
